Updates for 18.04

openjdk-8-jre-headless instead of openjdk-7-jre-headless
add libffi-dev to plone_instances
replace liblcms1-dev with liblcms2-dev
replace libtiff4-dev with libtiff5-dev
replace recipe redis::default with plone_buildout::redis in Redis layer

Disable auto Elastic IPs for HAProxy and Shared Blob layers
Disable OS updates on boot for all layers:

for layer_id in $(aws opsworks describe-layers --region us-east-1 --stack-id $stack_id --output text --query 'Layers[*].[LayerId]')
do
    aws opsworks update-layer --layer-id $layer_id --no-install-updates-on-boot --region us-east-1
done
